p.01703376c4a81c0e9d91: Trims whitespace from the beginning and end of the string
p.01703376c4a81c0e9d92: Removes whitespace from both ends of a string. Whitespace in this context is all the whitespace characters (space, tab, no-break space, etc.) and all the line terminator characters (LF, CR, etc.). Uses the `trim` JavaScript function. See string object
